name: Create a scheduled post using new button

elements.name: As a user I create a scheduled post using New post button on posts list

steps.name: I set scenario "Post_creation_scheduled" and version app "<VERSION>"
I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having xpath "//a[@href='#/posts/']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-btn.gh-btn-green.ember-view"
I enter "$name_1" into input field having css selector ".gh-editor-title"
I enter "$name_2" into input field having css selector ".koenig-editor__editor"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-publishmenu"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-date-time-picker"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-publishmenu-button"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/posts/']"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-contentfilter-type"
I click on element having css selector "li[data-option-index='3']"
